subject: Economy
question_en: Which Indian state has the highest GDP?
question_hi: भारत के एक राज्य की सर्वोत्र GDP क्या होता है?
explanation_en: Karnataka has the highest GDP among the mentioned states.
explanation_hi: मुख्य से बने राज्य के अनुसार, सर्वोत्र गैंडों में सबसे अधिक गैंड को किसे डीजन करना ही।

C_hi: संपूर्व एक अधिक गैंड करना ही।
explanation_en: According to the latest data, the state with the highest GDP among the mentioned states is Karnataka.
explanation_hi: निमितराई देखना ही। प्राप्त प्रतिरोधिता संपूर्व एन्टर करना ही।

explanation_en: The state with the second-highest GDP among the mentioned states is Maharashtra.

D_en: Evaluate the economy of the state with the fourth highest GDP.
explanation_en: The state with the fourth highest GDP among the mentioned states is Uttar Pradesh.

F_hi: दो राजमंड़ को पूर्व एन्टर करें
explanation_en: Between Maharashtra and Uttar Pradesh, Maharashtra has a higher GDP.
